        <updateDate>2019-08-29T14:43:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Contaminant and Lead Electronic Accounting and Reporting Requirements (CLEARR) for Drinking Water Act of 2018</strong></p> <p>This bill assists communities in complying with and reporting on drinking water requirements, including to reauthorize&nbsp;through FY2023 a grant program for assisting the public water systems of small&nbsp;or disadvantaged communities comply with drinking water requirements.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
